 Review comment:
   When you say "partition", do you mean "partition expression"? Which const correctness is removed? If we wait until invocation of the filter kernel to simplify the selector then we lose the opportunity to exclude data sources based on their partition expression: using Assume (which simplifies the expression) can yield trivially false, allowing us to skip that data source.

